117698; Su, J.Z., (1999) Technical Report IRC-IR-812, , http://www.irc.nrc-cnrc.gc.ca, National Research Council, Canada <http://www.irc.nrc-cnrc.gc.ca>; De Vos, R., Dams, R.J., Process for the preparation of rigid polyurethane foams (1998), European Patent No. EP0809671/1998Handa, Y.P., Francis, G.A., Thermoplastic foams made with methyl-formate-based blowing agents (2007), US Patent No. 7307105Environment Canada and Health Canada, Priority Substances List Assessment Report: Acetaldehyde, Technical Report, Canadian Environmental Protection Act, 2000. <http://www.hc-sc.gc.ca/ewh-semt/alt_formats/hecs-sesc/pdf/pubs/contaminants/psl2-lsp2/acetaldehyde/acetaldehyde_fin-eng.pdf>","Linke, P.; Chemical Engineering Department, Texas A and M University at Qatar, P.O. Box 23874, Doha, Qatar; email: patrick.linke@qatar.tamu.edu",,,,,,,,13594311,,ATENF,,"English","Appl Therm Eng",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-76449090380
